## Deploy safety

1. **Local PC:** build + upload
2. **hPanel:** Node.js Restart only — [hpanel.hostinger.com](https://hpanel.hostinger.com/)
3. **Two-folder model:** FTPS staging → sync → live root
4. **Never** run upload scripts in hPanel Terminal

## MCP

`HOSTINGER_API_TOKEN` in `.env.local` → `npm run sync:mcp-env` → global `hostinger-*` servers.

